{"title":"西沙群岛散歌","authors":["蔡其矫"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":6,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"西沙群岛散歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔡其矫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白浪的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白浪唱着歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在远方的礁盘上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有久积的愤怒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在它热情的歌中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我看见外国的强盗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霸占孤零的海岛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见祖国的渔夫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血染悲伤的珊瑚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我带来他们的血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻找祖国的旗申诉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要走到那旗下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向战士求保护。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我唱的是祈求的歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼吁正义快快来到！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由快快来到！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光明快快来到！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有月亮的晚间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么海岛一片光明？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是云在辉耀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是浪在返照？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见每一珊瑚碎片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都如珍珠般闪烁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南海的夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是青春年华的裸胸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那光洁的肌肤下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗处女的心在跳动；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它整夜朝着北斗星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诉说着万年的爱情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他在心头贮存整个祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色的海岸，粼粼的水波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有亲爱的颜脸在竹帘后。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当他凭栏站在甲板上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见这一切都浮起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在他那光闪闪的眼里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他见过非洲的沙岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也见过南洋的椰子林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都觉得不如自己的称心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因此他来到南海的荒岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深情地注视海岸，注视水波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛那亲爱的颜脸也在树后藏着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开发者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在黑龙江的森林里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是土地的保卫者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是一个士兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在南海的孤岛上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是海洋的看门人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是一个开发者。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见你收集各种彩色的商标，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见你收集全世界的邮票。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在你又在发现鸟类和贝壳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是在发现生活。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热爱人类智慧的创作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热爱自然美丽的生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是士兵的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是开发者的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女医生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在海岛的更楼上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南方的夜白茫茫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在少女的心中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱情在歌唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她还未恋爱过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就把心给开拓南海的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一句情话也没有说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用手指，用倾听来爱抚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花香和波光的夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无声地照耀在岛上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"博爱和深情的海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无声地闪烁在她眸子中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔捞员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在蓝海的深处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星贝闪闪发光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在黎明的山谷中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喷出一千支泉水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在月光的庭院里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开放一千朵玫瑰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把泉水送给孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把玫瑰留交少女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使海的色泽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化为爱的光辉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就因为这你们捞取着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在含辛茹苦的大海里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩色的海螺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人们送给我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个彩色的海螺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的上面描绘着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热带海洋蓝色的水波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其中飘动绿的海藻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金的鱼群，银的珊瑚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的里面却在讴歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个英勇的战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交织着巨浪的怒吼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是正义的伸张，自由的开拓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的眼睛注视南海的水波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心震响着南海的战歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过万里风涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走上天涯海角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三百工人足踩珊瑚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为南海打开黎明的路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我记得彩霞飞鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我记得星光船舶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我记得热情的工人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临别时对我咐托。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！光明的珊瑚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！渺茫的烟波！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么时候我的足迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再走到你的尽头？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1957年4月24日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}